Instance Method

handle(call:result:)

Handles the method calls from Flutter.

Declaration

func handle(call: FlutterMethodCall, result: @escaping FlutterResult)

Discussion

When calling TIKI SDK Flutter from native code, one should pass a requestId that will identify to which request the response belongs to. All the calls are asynchronous and should be treated like this.
